metadata.name: 01C-69Land-31Mountains-44Sea-41Sky
metadata.description:
01C-69Land-31Mountains-44Sea-41Sky is a unique artwork from Land Sea and Sky by Jennifer and Kevin McCoy, a collection of enigmatic landscape collages built by combining compositional forms based on iconic 20th-century landscape photography with AI-generated imagery of the American countryside. 

Land Sea and Sky was commissioned by Artwrld.
